flowchart TD
    Start([horizon status]) --> CheckInstalled{Service installed?}
    
    CheckInstalled -->|No| NotInstalled[Warn: Not installed]
    NotInstalled --> SuggestInstall[Suggest horizon install]
    SuggestInstall --> SuccessExit([Success])
    
    CheckInstalled -->|Yes| CheckRunning{Currently running?}
    
    CheckRunning -->|Yes| ReportRunning[Info: Horizon is running]
    ReportRunning --> SuccessExit
    
    CheckRunning -->|No| ReportStopped[Warn: Not running]
    ReportStopped --> SuggestStart[Suggest horizon start]
    SuggestStart --> SuccessExit
